like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T18:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/023210_f22073c0a15ce5d98b81e9ad9b0f2930.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F023210_f22073c0a15ce5d98b81e9ad9b0f2930.jpg&h=0c978ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好意思原來我貼錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T18:56:08.000Z","msg":"JBAT1: Clear CMOS (Reset BIOS) Jumper<br />\nThere is CMOS memory onboard that is external powered from a battery located on the motherboard to save system configuration data. If you want to clear the system configuration, set the jumpers to clear the CMOS memory.<br />\nKeep Data Clear CMOS/ Reset (default) BIOS<br />\nResetting BIOS to default values<br />\n1. Power off the computer and unplug the power cord<br />\n2. Use a jumper cap to short JBAT1 for about 5-10 seconds.<br />\n3. Remove the jumper cap from JBAT1.<br />\n4. Plug the power cord and power on the computer.<br />\n你呢塊板要睇manual去short jumper"},{"pid":"7c863bca16eab2cf15ae3f02a2ce177c9110e02a","tid":718372,"uid":116596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e01569fdab3b5cf52ad2f6a628ae8758507c17","tid":718372,"uid":55725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71178bea3beaab2be3d5922503288d0d4a7c0618","tid":718372,"uid":116596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T18:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/023210_f22073c0a15ce5d98b81e9ad9b0f2930.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F023210_f22073c0a15ce5d98b81e9ad9b0f2930.jpg&h=0c978ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好意思原來我貼錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T18:56:08.000Z","msg":"JBAT1: Clear CMOS (Reset BIOS) Jumper<br />\nThere is CMOS memory onboard that is external powered from a battery located on the motherboard to save system configuration data. If you want to clear the system configuration, set the jumpers to clear the CMOS memory.<br />\nKeep Data Clear CMOS/ Reset (default) BIOS<br />\nResetting BIOS to default values<br />\n1. Power off the computer and unplug the power cord<br />\n2. Use a jumper cap to short JBAT1 for about 5-10 seconds.<br />\n3. Remove the jumper cap from JBAT1.<br />\n4. Plug the power cord and power on the computer.<br />\n你呢塊板要睇manual去short jumper"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:09:15.000Z","msg":"唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18c4630f8217ed61c572ac8b9cdc6d08f016c3d","tid":718372,"uid":150284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T02:56:32.000Z","msg":"試過同一情況 最後壞底板<br />\n都係ASROCK"},{"pid":"149cb89028673761cb8708d7dfa9fea980a3b0d4","tid":718372,"uid":116596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c18c4630f8217ed61c572ac8b9cdc6d08f016c3d","tid":718372,"uid":150284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T02:56:32.000Z","msg":"試過同一情況 最後壞底板<br />\n都係ASROCK"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:17:06.000Z","msg":"我貼錯list<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561431b881ed091e7548690215f8321d187751e2","tid":718372,"uid":116596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"更新下今朝又無啦啦開到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063ee3fc7561392248b6811a46a41c9d50bf173c","tid":718372,"uid":116596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"今朝開到用到 晚上又用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 